{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"communicate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"stdinBuf","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib8BytesRefV","text":"BytesRef"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"stdoutBuf","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GBytes","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">?>? = nil, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"stderrBuf"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GBytes"},{"kind":"text","text":">?>? = nil) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"stdinBuf","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is given, the subprocess must have been created with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stdinPipe","type":"reference"},{"text":".  The given data is fed to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"stdin of the subprocess and the pipe is closed (ie: EOF)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"At the same time (as not to cause blocking when dealing with large","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"amounts of data), if "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stdoutPipe","type":"reference"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stderrPipe","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" were used, reads from those"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"streams.  The data that was read is returned in ","type":"text"},{"code":"stdout","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and\/or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stderr"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the subprocess was created with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stdoutPipe","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"stdoutBuf","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will contain the data read from stdout.  Otherwise, for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subprocesses not created with "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stdoutPipe","isActive":true},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stdoutBuf"},{"text":" will be set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":".  Similar provisions apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stderrBuf"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stderrPipe","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As usual, any output variable may be given as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" to ignore it.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you desire the stdout and stderr data to be interleaved, create"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the subprocess with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/stdoutPipe","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stderrMerge"},{"text":".  The merged result will be returned","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stdoutBuf"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stderrBuf"},{"text":" will be set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In case of any error (including cancellation), "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"text":" will be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returned with "},{"code":"error","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" set.  Some or all of the stdin data may have","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"been written.  Any stdout or stderr data that has been read will be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"discarded. None of the out variables (aside from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":") will have"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"been set to anything in particular and should not be inspected."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the case that "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned, the subprocess has exited and the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"exit status inspection APIs (eg: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_subprocess_get_if_exited()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_subprocess_get_exit_status()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") may be used.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should not attempt to use any of the subprocess pipes after"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"starting this function, since they may be left in strange states,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"even if the operation was cancelled.  You should especially not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempt to interact with the pipes while the operation is in progress"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(either from another thread or if using the asynchronous version).","type":"text"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/SubprocessProtocol-Implementations"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessRef\/communicate(stdinBuf:cancellable:stdoutBuf:stderrBuf:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"communicate(stdinBuf:cancellable:stdoutBuf:stderrBuf:)","externalID":"s:3GIO18SubprocessProtocolPAAE11communicate8stdinBuf11cancellable06stdoutF006stderrF0Sb4GLib8BytesRefVSg_AA011CancellableL0VSgSpySpySo7_GBytesVGSgGSgAUtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO13SubprocessRefV","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GIO","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"communicate"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"stdinBuf","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib8BytesRefV","text":"BytesRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},